projectDescription: The Choir Ministry has been faithfully serving OECT for the past decade! If you are a choir member, and would like to access the resources, you must first sign up and register for a OECT membership. You can begin registration here! Once approved, you will have access to the Choir Material! This is to ensure that privacy, security, and integrity is maintained for all our internal resources. Thank you! If you are already a OECT Church member, and would like to access the choir material, click here.
Amplified For Christ is our youth program at OECT that longs to share the Gospel, encourage students to live out their faith, share their faith and be apart of the larger church community.
